qa_list.question: When and where is the Tartan Men's Cross Country Schedule?
qa_list.answer: The schedule for the 2023 Tartan Men's Cross Country includes events in September, October, and November. The first event is on Friday, September 1st at AT Panther Opener held at Schenley Park in Pittsburgh, Pa.

qa_list.question: What was the result of the Tartan Men's Cross Country team at Dickinson Long-Short Invitational?
qa_list.answer: The Tartan Men's Cross Country team finished 1st in the 8k race and 3rd in the 4k race at the Dickinson Long-Short Invitational held on Saturday, September 23rd at Big Spring High School in Newville, Pa.

qa_list.question: Where was the Paul Short Invitational held?
qa_list.answer: The Paul Short Invitational took place on Saturday, October 7th at Lehigh University in Bethlehem, Pa.

qa_list.question: What is the date and time of Carnegie Mellon Invitational?
qa_list.answer: Carnegie Mellon Invitational will be held on Saturday, October 7th at 10:00 a.m. at Schenley Park in Pittsburgh, Pa.

qa_list.question: Where was the SUNY Geneseo Mike Woods Invitational held?
qa_list.answer: The Tartan Men's Cross Country team competed at the SUNY Geneseo Mike Woods Invitational on Saturday, October 14th at Schenley Park in Pittsburgh, Pa.

qa_list.question: Where was UAA Championships held?
qa_list.answer: The Tartan Men's Cross Country team participated in the UAA Championships on Saturday, October 28th at Case Western Reserve University in Cleveland, Ohio.

qa_list.question: When and where is Lock Haven NCAA Mid-Atlantic Regional?
qa_list.answer: The Tartan Men's Cross Country team will compete at the Lock Haven NCAA Mid-Atlantic Regional on Saturday, November 11th at 11:00 a.m. in Lock Haven, Pa.

qa_list.question: Where is the final event of Tartan Men's Cross Country Schedule?
qa_list.answer: The last event on the schedule for the 2023 Tartan Men's Cross Country is at Big Spring High School in Newville, Pa. on Saturday, November 18th.

qa_list.question: What was the result of the Tartan Men's Cross Country team at NCAA Championships?
qa_list.answer: The Tartan Men's Cross Country team finished 6th out of 32 teams at the NCAA Championships held on Saturday, November 18th at Big Spring High School in Newville, Pa.
